                 |When you drop off your vehicle to a body shop, make sure asking them some questions about how do they take care your vehicle?
                <ul>
                    <li>Washing your vehicle before dropping off</li>
                    <li>Taking more photos and pay attention about prior damages.</li>
                </ul>
